<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2626777>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Cancricepon beibusinus n. sp., holotype female (MBMCAS CIEO 625301) (A–J), allotype male (MBMCAS CIEO 625302) (K–N): A, dorsal view; B, ventral view; C, right antennule and antenna; D, right maxilliped, external view; E, barbula; F, right oostegite 1, external view; G, right oostegite 1, internal view; H, right pereopod 2; I, right pereopod 7; J, right pleopod 1; K, dorsal view; L, ventral view; M, left antennule and antenna; N, left pereopod 1. Scale bars: A, B, K, L = 1 mm; C = 220 µm; D = 410 µm; E = 550 µm; F, G, J = 730 µm; H, I = 280 µm; M, N = 125µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2626777/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

